<br>
1 - play along with scammer for a minute and type /who all GM<br>
<br>
2 - send a tell to a level 50+ GM. Tell them a scammer is connected at that very moment and trying to cheat you. Tell the guide that you'll open a petition, but that you want them to get the scammer's account info for their records before he disconnects.<br>
<br>
3 - type /report "scammer name" every few lines that the scammer says, and it will flag all that text for the GM to read.<br>
<br>
4 - type /petition "Scammer name" is trying to scam me. "Guide name" should have his account info, and I /report'd everything the scammer said to me. Thank you for your time. :) (or something like that, hehe)<br>
<br>
They probably won't be able to get him right then, but at least we'll have helped our guide staff get all the information we can to set this jerk up and nail him.<br>
<br>
